o-sue-meta-over-threads-3466298">Twitter 威胁要就 Meta 的发布提起诉讼</a>。</p><p>本月，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/grimes">格莱姆斯</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/grimes-says-she-proposed-the-idea-of-elon-musks-dick-measuring-challenge-3480396">透露，她提出了前合伙人马斯克向扎克伯格提出的“真正的阴茎测量竞赛”的想法</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/mark-zuckerberg-appears-to-call-off-cage-fight-with-elon-musk-3482082">马克·扎克伯格似乎取消了与埃隆·马斯克的笼斗：“是时候继续前进了”，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
 Chuck D 讲述有关嘻哈音乐诞生的新音频纪录片https://www.nme.com/news/music/chuck-d-narrates-new-audio-docu-drama-about-the-birth-of-hip-hop-3482079?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=chuck- d-叙述关于嘻哈诞生的新音频纪录片戏剧Hollie GeraghtySun, 13 Aug 2023 18:09:59 +0000 Music NewsNewsHip-hop https://www.nme.com/?p=3482079 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/chuck-d-hip-hop-series.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/chuck-d-hip-hop-series.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/chuck-d-hip-hop-series-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/chuck-d-hip-hop-series-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/chuck-d-hip-hop-series-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/chuck-d-hip-hop-series-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/chuck-d-hip-hop-series-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位公敌主唱在五集剧集“Can You Dig It?”中回顾了嘻哈音乐的崛起</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chuck-d-narrates-new-audio-docu-drama-about-the-birth-of-hip-hop-3482079">Chuck D 讲述有关嘻哈音乐诞生的新音频纪录片的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/chuck-d-hip-hop-series.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/chuck-d-hip-hop-series.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/chuck-d-hip-hop-series-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/chuck-d-hip-hop-series-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/chuck-d-hip-hop-series-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/chuck-d-hip-hop-series-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/chuck-d-hip-hop-series-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/public-enemy">Chuck D</a>为一部关于嘻哈音乐兴起的新音频纪录片系列进行了旁白，现已可供收听。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/public-enemy-chuck-d-interview-state-of-the-union-stfu-flava-flav-new-album-2697798">公敌的 Chuck D：“行动主义是在被证明你没有权力之后出现的”</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位美国说唱歌手兼<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/public-enemy">Public Enemy</a>主唱在新剧集<em>Can You Dig It?</em>中讲述了 20 世纪 60 年代末和 70 年代初嘻哈音乐在纽约布朗克斯诞生的故事。<em>嘻哈起源故事。</em></p><p>根据该剧的摘要，这位嘻哈先锋在 5 集 30 分钟的剧集中，通过“身临其境的重演、口述历史和专家讨论”的结合，回顾了这一流派的崛起。</p><p> “嘻哈音乐是如何产生的？为了理解这一点，我们必须回到文化诞生之前，”描述中写道。 </p><figure id="attachment_3435370" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3435370" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3435370" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Chuck-D-and-Tupac.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Chuck-D-and-Tupac.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Chuck-D-and-Tupac-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Chuck-D-and-Tupac-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Chuck-D-and-Tupac-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Chuck-D-and-Tupac-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Chuck-D-and-Tupac-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3435370" class="wp-caption-text">查克·D 和图帕克。图片来源：Al Pereira/Michael Ochs Archives/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p>它继续说道：“20 世纪 60 年代末和 70 年代初的布朗克斯并不是一种美国艺术形式的诞生地。城市重建使该行政区被忽视并陷入危机。街头有帮派维持治安，如果在错误的地区出现可能会造成严重后果。但事情即将发生变化。”</p><p>正如现场人士所说，它将这些塞雷斯描述为“积极的社区影响如何帮助激励陷入困境的年轻人结束帮派暴力循环的深入历史”。</p><p>剧情简介补充道：“这是一个鼓舞人心的真实故事，讲述了当地帮派贫民窟兄弟在 Black Benjie（一名试图寻找共同点的成员）被谋杀后如何拒绝战争的呼吁，以及帮派头目 Yellow Benjy 和空手道查理如何努力与竞争对手达成和平。最终结果是？在这里，城市艺术可以蓬勃发展，发展成为持续 50 年的全球文化：嘻哈。”</p><p>谈到他参与这个项目时，Chuck D 告诉<em><a href="https://www.billboard.com/music/rb-hip-hop/chuck-d-can-you-dig-it-hip-hop-50-1235387458/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Billboard</a></em> ：“但是当我开始剥开它时，我想，‘哇，这就是故事背后的故事。’”这是种子的发芽，嘻哈音乐的开始。</p><p> “我们总是可以宽松地谈论‘当帮派停止时嘻哈就开始了，然后突然他们使用了嘻哈。’”但这些都是粗略的描述，并且充满了神话色彩。这个[系列]详细介绍了什么是什么。你几乎可以在废墟上闻到跨布朗克斯高速公路新鲜油漆的味道。”</p><p>该系列节目现已可<a href="https://www.audible.co.uk/?ref=Adbl_ip_rdr_from_US&amp;source_code=AUK30DFT1BkWS0826159058&amp;ipRedirectFrom=US&amp;ipRedirectOriginalURL=pd%2FCan-You-Dig-It-Podcast%2FB0CBCW31N8" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在 Audible 上收听</a>。</p><p>早在去年 12 月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chuck-d-says-public-enemy-were-harassed-by-the-police-more-than-anyone-in-music-3372646">Chuck D 就曾表示，Public Enemy “受到警察的骚扰比音乐界的任何人都多”</a> 。</p><p>他最近还讲述了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tupac">图帕克</a>出于对公敌的忠诚而殴打小偷的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tupac-beat-up-a-thief-out-of-loyalty-to-public-enemy-says-chuck-d-sway-in-the-morning-3435343">故事</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chuck-d-narrates-new-audio-docu-drama-about-the-birth-of-hip-hop-3482079">Chuck D 讲述有关嘻哈音乐诞生的新音频纪录片的</a>帖子首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
